# LiveFlare

Live stream monitor & alert app for Windows.

![LiveFlare main window](screenshots/main-window.png)

## Features
- Real-time online status display
- Desktop toast notifications when stream starts
- 13 language support(EN / JA / KO / ZH-CN / ZH-TW / DE / FR / ES / PT / RU / TH / VI / ID)
- System tray background operation

## Supported Platforms
YouTube / Twitch / Kick / TwitCasting / FC2 Live

## Requirements
Windows 10/11 (64bit)

## Download
[Latest Release](https://github.com/daigorou-addon/LiveFlare/releases/latest)

## Related Extensions
- [PPP Live Alert](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/bejlnfnhfgkaddplnkcnhgmoacineode) - YouTube / Twitch / Kick (Chrome/Edge)
- [FC2ライブ検索ふくにくん](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/ghkobnmkiieaaolppjlgbmhbdlnjgfjc) - FC2 Live (Chrome/Edge)

A Windows SmartScreen warning may appear during installation.
Click "More info" → "Run anyway". This is safe software made by an indie developer.
